{"tid":2167031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國幾時開始制裁黨鐵高層人員？","createTime":"2020-08-20T20:50:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T22:01:56.000Z","uid":220066,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f5c3d55b2a661da41fc57fe7177467f8f7c844e0","tid":2167031,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T20:50:36.000Z","msg":"雖然美國宣布制裁十一位官員<br />\n令到佢地而家生活上出現「唔方便」情況<br />\n我想講美國唔好忘記要制裁黨鐵呢班高層人員<br />\n佢地完全無交代721 831  CCTV 片段出嚟<br />\n好明顯係協助港共隱滿真相<br />\n上年721 831 有好多手足<br />\n市民都被黑社會無差別打傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n港鐵高層人員可以視而不見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n企圖危害全港市民生命財產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直到至今仍然唔交代721 831 當晚情況<br />\n唔該美國下一步盡快制裁所有港鐵高層人員<br />\n佢地一定會係外國擁有大量資產<br />\n希望打緊國際線手足可以留意<br />\n唔好忘記黨鐵所有高層人員<br />\n盡快凍結呢班人資產<br />\n我要佢地永遠效忠中華人民共和國🇨🇳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06869c0f678a3b53b422aed41414ab5ea5431d04","tid":2167031,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T20:52:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c090797c4a676054f7dd92c51bf613b5649110a","tid":2167031,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T20:54:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a83d9b4b5e363f7c92df63cef892a784e92fb7b8","tid":2167031,"uid":6589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T20:56:31.000Z","msg":"巴打放twitter美國先會見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1f93d0ff0289f5d3b15bdfac6d2af949f3adeb7","tid":2167031,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T21:01:17.000Z","msg":"可唔可以幫我？"},{"pid":"6d3119dbd745c37742618f56496c99998add7e5b","tid":2167031,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T21:01:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face